Validates a growth chart code

Source: R/validate_chartcode.R
validate_chartcode.Rd

This function checks whether chartcode is a available in the chart library.

Usage

validate_chartcode(chartcode = "", ...)

Arguments

chartcode

Chart code, typically something like "NMAB"

...

Used for authentication

Value

A logical vector of with length(chartcode) elements.

See also

list_charts()
